<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Question Reply</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .question-box {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 10px;
        border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .reply-box {
        background-color: #e9f7ef;
        padding: 10px;
        border-left: 4px solid #2ecc71;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #888;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Response to Your Question</h1>

      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for asking a question in the course. We value your
        participation and are glad to provide an answer.
      </p>

      <div class="question-box">
        <strong>Your Question:</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="reply-box">
        <strong>Our Reply:</strong>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have further questions or need more clarification, feel free to
        reply to this email or ask another question in the course forum.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
